00:37:15,269 --> 00:37:16,730
at a minimum of each one of those.

442
00:37:17,510 --> 00:37:22,833
So what I did is I looked at the law and I found it on page, it's section 18.

443
00:37:23,773 --> 00:37:25,714
Larry, he's not here when he comes back.

444
00:37:27,095 --> 00:37:34,258
