454
00:39:05,028 --> 00:39:07,649
At the end of the fifth year, it automatically dies.

455
00:39:08,389 --> 00:39:18,353
If, in fact, the people of this community and whoever the council might be at that time wishes to go forward and renew it again for another five years, then the question goes on the ballot.

456
00:39:19,073 --> 00:39:22,755
You are dealing with right now your second fiscal year on this CPA.

457
00:39:23,635 --> 00:39:28,397
I don't think any one of you behind this rail have even been informed as to where and how that money is going to be spent.

458
00:39:28,835 --> 00:39:30,857
