462
00:39:37,944 --> 00:39:43,029
There's a great latitude that up to a nine-member board or a commission has with that money.

463
00:39:43,830 --> 00:39:46,072
And you as a council haven't even been right into the picture.

464
00:39:46,632 --> 00:39:50,396
