1126
01:28:34,642 --> 01:28:48,726
This particular ordinance was something that was proposed back in 2011 to address concerns of companies coming into this community and erecting cell towers in residential areas.

1127
01:28:49,486 --> 01:28:53,647
And at the time we put together, I believe it was a seven or eight page ordinance,

1128
01:28:54,278 --> 01:29:05,028
